import React from 'react'; import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet-async'; import './NaturalRubberSBR.css'; import nrSbrImage from '../assets/images/nr-sbr-sheeting.png'; function NaturalRubberSBR() { return (
Natural Rubber / SBR Sheeting - Zenith Rubber

Natural Rubber / SBR Sheeting

NR/SBR is commonly used in various industries due to its versatile properties and cost-effectiveness. The blend provides superior resilience, tensile, elongation, good low temperature flexibility and excellent adhesion to fabric and metals.

NR/SBR is widely used in general purpose seals & gaskets, washers, packing material, vibration dampeners, shot blasting curtains and for industrial purpose application in contact with water and oil free surfaces and in various sectors like Automotive, Construction, Industrial Belts, Machinery, Sports & Recreation etc.

ZENA-FLEX NR/SBR RUBBER SHEETS

Code Colour Specific Gravity Gm/cm³ Hardness (±5) SHORE A Tensile Strength Kg/cm2(min) Elongation % (min) Finish Type TDS
NR/SBR 60130 Black 1.3 60 50 250 Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 65135 Black, Offwhite, Brick Red 1.35 65 50 250 Smooth/Fabric
AD70148 Black 1.5 70 35 200 Smooth/Matt -
SX70150 Black 1.5 70 30 200 Smooth/Fabric -
NR/SBR 70155 Black 1.55 70 30 200 Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 70160 Black 1.6 70 30 200 Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 70161 Black 1.60 70 30 200 with 1 ply fabric insertion
NR/SBR 70162 Black 1.60 70 30 200 with 2 ply Fabric Insertion
NR/SBR 70190 offwhite 1.9 70 15 130% Fabric/Fabric
NR/SBR 75210 Black 2.1 75 15 150 Fabric/Fabric

SHOT BLASTING RUBBER SHEET

Zena Blast ECO

Code Colour Specific Gravity Hardness (±5) SHORE A Tensile Strength Kg/cm2(min) Elongation % (min) Finish Type TDS
NR/SBR 45130 Black, Offwhite, Red 1.30 45 50 250 Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 55132 Black, Offwhite, Red 1.32 55 50 250 Smooth/Fabric

Zena Blast Standard

Code Colour Specific Gravity Hardness (±5) SHORE A Tensile Strength Kg/cm2(min) Elongation % (min) Finish Type TDS
NR/SBR 45125 Black & Brick Red 1.25 45 100 450% Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 65125 Black 1.25 65 100 350 Smooth/Fabric

Zena Blast Pro

Code Colour Specific Gravity Hardness (±5) SHORE A Tensile Strength Kg/cm2(min) Elongation % (min) Finish Type TDS
NR/SBR 40110 Black, Pink, Orange 1.10 40 165 600 Smooth/Fabric
NR/SBR 60110 Black 1.10 60 150 500 Smooth/Fabric

NATURAL RUBBER SHEETS - FOOD GRADE

Code Colour Specific Gravity Hardness (±5) SHORE A Tensile Strength Kg/cm2(min) Elongation % (min) Polymer content TDS
SB 65150 FG Offwhite 1.50 65 40 250 NR/SBR

Standard Sizes

Standard Length: 10 Mtr / 33 Ft

Standard Width: 1.2 / 1.4 / 1.5 / 2 Mtr / 4 / 4.6 / 4.92 / 6.56 Ft

Standard Yard: 1.33 / 1.53 / 1.64 / 2.18 Yard

Note

  1. Sheets can be supplied with 1 or 2 ply insertion/s in Cotton, Nylon, Polyester, Glass Fibre etc.
  2. One side or both side smooth or fabric finish can be supplied.
  3. Specifications are subject to change without notice.
); } export default NaturalRubberSBR;
